Hi!

I seem to have frequent problems with objectives registering. For example, required parts sometimes doesn't register until I have launched a vessel, then gone to space center and back to the vessel. 

Orbits seems to be the most difficult. The following objectives didn't register at the first attempt, after reloading the went green, but now they are back grey again.

Any ideas why this is happening?
